          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣要保只保小千岁"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军你呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那卞庄好似得胜的猫儿强似虎"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幼主爷龙困沙滩难翻转"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣要保只保小千岁"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斗宝曾在临潼会，"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万马营中逞雄威。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不怨将军怨着谁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保皇家四口丧两口"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子胥闻说忙屈膝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢国太。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊声国太驾听知："
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为臣的四十少二春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知者反说臣的……"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龙国太今年三十二"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道的自说臣保主"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个“妻”字未出唇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国太面上怒气生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍天岂容我伍员。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子胥若有欺天意"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被他一言来提醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提醒南柯梦里人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "容我母子暗思忖。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "独坐在大佛殿自思自恨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怀抱着年幼儿大放悲声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父纳了子的妻败坏人伦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "连累了伍将军丧胆游魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奔天涯走地角凄凄惨惨无处安身。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后面来了保驾臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国太快快设计行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迈步且把禅堂进"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人言子胥是好将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日果然不虚名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太子付与将军抱"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扬尘舞蹈接王身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别国太便登程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解开甲胄藏幼主"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手拿金枪踏金蹬"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请转。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国太有话快说明！"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不当将军保太子，"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "直当将军你自己生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国太不必细叮咛，"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君是君来臣是臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放我君臣早逃生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国太快把良谋定"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍天降下无情剑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩断母子两离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将身跳在葵花井！"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国太快把良谋定"
        },
        {
          "character": "国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，那旁有人来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（国太跳井，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见国太丧了命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子胥倒做不忠臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卞庄上，卞庄、伍员同开打，伍员败下。四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那贼大败！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卞庄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "紧紧追赶！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
